Templates:
    base.html - base page with navbar and footer
    dishes/dashboard.html - landing page displaying dishes
    dishes/dish.html - new dish form/update dish form
    dishes/ratings-form.html - snippet containing a ratings form for a dish 
    dishes/dish-details.html - dish details page
    dishes/favorites.html - list of favorite dishes
    dishes/categories - list categories
    dishes/category.html - category details
    dishes/card-dish.html
    card_dish - cards for displaying dishes
    card_category - card for displaying categories
    chip_category - chip for displaying lists of categories on recipe page
    chip_user - chip for displaying list of users on recipe page

chef (user) routes
- chefs - display all users
- chefs/<int:user_id> - user details
- chefs/registration - 
- chefs/login - 
- chefs/<int:user_id>/update
- chefs/<int:user_id>/follow
- chefs/<int:user_id>/un_follow

Profile page
- recipes favorited
- recipes made ("I made it")
- reviews
- personal recipes (created)
- followers
- following

Favicon 
add these links to the head section of your base.html page
<link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="/apple-touch-icon.png">
<link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/favicon-32x32.png">
<link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="/favicon-16x16.png">
<link rel="manifest" href="/site.webmanifest">

