Idea- password strength meter 
- zxcvbn library for password validation
    include this in a script tag in the template: https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/zxcvbn/4.4.2/zxcvbn.js
    CSS Tricks: Password Strength `meter` https://css-tricks.com/password-strength-meter/

- Password Strength Indicator using jQuery
   https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/password-strength-indicator-using-jquery/

- jQuery Plugin For Password Strength Checker and Indicator - Password-Strength
    https://www.jqueryscript.net/form/jQuery-Plugin-For-Password-Strength-Checker-and-Indicator-Password-Strength.html
    https://www.jqueryscript.net/demo/jQuery-Plugin-For-Password-Strength-Checker-and-Indicator-Password-Strength

- other ideas: https://www.jqueryscript.net/blog/best-password-strength-checker.html